value.0: Hardened by the hostile environment, trained extensively and outfitted with high quality equipment, the men and women of the Forrstakkr Guard are a more than capable fighting force in the harsh northern environment. Augmented by veterans from the Ostland conflict, this force is quite ready to protect and fight for the people of Forrstakkr.

Value.value: Vigilant One, Great Guardian, hear me!
Lord Helm, shining bright in the darkness, Bearer of Brisingamen, hear me!
God's blessing-maker, given as oath-bond, Helm of the firth-stead, hear me!
To Midgard's ring I rown thee forth, on Hildisvin's back, Mardöll, to me!
Wain-god mighty, wend thy way here, I call thee at need, come here to my stead.
To Midgard's ring I rown thee forth, in falcon-cloak from Folkvang, Helm, to me!
I bid thee with horn of holy drink. Welcome, O Watcher, to me!
Horn this horn is hallowed to thee, Helm. Blessed I raise it, and bid thee to share.
